## 11. Security & Risk Disclosures

- No private key or seed phrase is ever stored in a Lemma table, sent to a Lemma Function, or logged anywhere — full stop. The only wallet data persisted is a public address.
- The submitted build executes trades in **simulated mode only**. No real funds move.
- Net-profit estimates are pre-trade calculations based on fee/slippage assumptions you control — they are not a guarantee of realized profit, and real execution risk (price movement between legs, MEV, partial fills) is not eliminated by this check.
- This document and codebase are not financial or legal advice. Treat any path toward live execution as requiring its own security review before real funds touch it.

